com.metreeca.mill.tasks.xml

Class XML<T extends XML<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.metreeca.mill.tasks.xml.XML<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Task
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    XQuery, XSLT

    public abstract class XML<T extends XML<T>>
extends Object
implements Task
    XML abstract processing tasks.

    For each feed cell focused on a IRI:

    • retrieves the content of the IRI from the network cache;
    • parses the retrieved content as XML, possibly using a user-supplied parser;
    • executes an XML transform using the parsed XML as context node and a processor(Tool.Loader, String) processor} provided by the concrete implementation;
    • for each item in the sequence returned by the transform, generates a cell according to the item type.

    Feed cells focused on blank nodes or literals are skipped with a warning.
